cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.MA 

The paper discusses a system for training machine learning models on mobile devices, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The system focuses on labeling data, which is a common task in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the challenges of dealing with unknown labels and non-stationary data, which are common issues in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data science (cs.DS). Finally, the system includes a runtime system for scheduling and executing workloads, which is related to multi-agent systems (cs.MA).
